library(dslabs) data(“mtcars”)
custom_summary <- function (carCustom) { meanValue <- mean(carCustom) std <- sd(carCustom) maxValue <- max(carCustom) minValue <- min(carCustom) medianValue <- median(carCustom) customStatistics <- list(minValue,maxValue,meanValue,medianValue,std) return (customStatistics) } customNames <- names(mtcars) for (customIndex in 1:11){ carCustom <- mtcars[,customIndex] customStatistics <- custom_summary(carCustom) print(customNames[customIndex]) print(customStatistics) }
qq <- apply(mtcars,2,custom_summary) print(qq)
